Added in View FlashCards

Merged ViewFlashCards and Add Flashcards
Merged ViewFlashCards and Add Flashcards

View Flashcards now listed, flashcards now have unique identifiers, pushing flashcards now index with the unique identifier. When viewing flashcards, searches by the identifier instead of writing and reading at a fixed spot in the database.
Added a second user menu
Added Settings tab and removed UID button in login page
Added Profile Tab
Added scrolling effects
All tabs are set up, Search Activity made.
Screen transitions added. Top bar added. Back navigation added. Cleaned up some UI.
Fixed an invalid token. Now buildable.
Search somewhat functioning, changed how tags are put into the database.
Added a missing file
Added ic_camera
Added custom listview for flashcards while searching
Added ability to add several tags to a set. Tags now show up on flashcard when displaying sets. Search now works with several tags in a set.
Adding sets to the database no longer sets a useless tag child.
Changed how sets are structured in the database again. Database structure should be finalized now.
Manage Set tab now displays all the Flashcard Info
Removed flashName in placing set in usersFlash branch.
Made a new view on flashcards with recyclerview and cardview.
Remade the Make a Flashcard set Activity.
Make a flashcard activity now adds the set to the database
Swiping left in the Make a set screen now deletes cards. Redid the preview a set screen.
Update screen now correctly updates the set in the database. Checks are in place to check if a set is valid before pushing.
Public and Private option now correctly works.
